and referee?

25:22.253 --> 25:23.221
No, we will be fine.

25:23.523 --> 25:24.991
We are fine.

25:25.727 --> 25:26.762
Everything is fine.

25:29.701 --> 25:32.239
Thank you, Herbert,
for making me breakfast.

25:33.308 --> 25:35.079
