for showing me to my apartment.

25:35.079 --> 25:37.851
Now, if you both wouldn't mind,
I just need to...

25:47.269 --> 25:49.642
Eat your breakfast
and get some sleep.

25:49.642 --> 25:51.311
Mr. Jaggers won't return
until after dark.

25:51.311 --> 25:53.682
