not quite yourself today, Pip.

26:35.833 --> 26:38.037
One day ago, I was safe
with Joe and Biddy.

26:40.944 --> 26:41.912
But now, I

26:43.983 --> 26:45.286
I am looking at a boiled egg,

26:45.286 --> 26:47.389
