I'd know that voice anywhere.

30:14.069 --> 30:15.405
Make your peace with God,
Mr. Compeyson.

30:16.107 --> 30:18.078
Gentlemen, if this man
does me harm,

30:18.078 --> 30:20.550
his name is Magwitch.
Abel Magwitch.

30:20.550 --> 30:22.452
Transportee.
Escaped from Norfolk Island.

30:24.591 --> 30:25.994
Magwitch, my friend,

30:25.994 --> 30:27.229
you are quite
the miracle worker.

30:29.100 --> 30:30.937
How the hell did you
track me down?

30:30.937 --> 30:33.007
Because a man like you
will always make enemies.

30:35.045 --> 30:37.182
I escaped the colony
the day after you did

30:38.619 --> 30:41.525
and followed a trail of men
you'd robbed and swindled.

30:43.361 --> 30:46.434
I read gold had been struck
in Bathurst beyond the pass.

30:46.869 --> 30:48.304
I knew you'd go there.

30:49.140 --> 30:50.408
I knew.

30:51.344 --> 30:54.049
Not to dig
but to swindle those that did.

30:57.991 --> 31:01.163
Magwitch, you know me well.

31:02.967 --> 31:05.138
A gold rush attracts
the simplest sort of men.

31:06.240 --> 31:08.177
Oh, taking gold from them
wasn't even a challenge.

31:10.382 --> 31:12.185
