it's not all yours to split.

31:30.389 --> 31:32.092
No need to talk of division.

31:33.127 --> 31:34.096
I'm not here for gold.

31:36.234 --> 31:38.070
I'm here for one thing.

31:39.039 --> 31:39.941
Vengeance.

31:43.716 --> 31:44.617
See you in hell, Compeyson.

31:49.159 --> 31:50.497
Fucking bast...

